rows.label: qst700903_msg0001
rows.name: The footprints end here.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0002
rows.name:
Did it climb the rock, or
did it fly away lightly...

rows.label: qst700903_msg0003
rows.name:
For something that leaves such
uncute footprints? It has wings?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0004
rows.name:
No, I just thought it
would be funny if it did.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0005
rows.name:
Um... it didn't just...
disappear, did it?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0006
rows.name:
No way. It's just some animal
or monster's doing. It's been
walking around in circles.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0007
rows.name:
You're right. There's no such
thing as ghosts, is there?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0008
rows.name: Oh my, could you be?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0009
rows.name:
N-Never mind. I was
just a little curious.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0010
rows.name:
...I see. Then it's probably
better not to talk about THAT.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0011
rows.name: Eh? Wh-What are you talking about?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0012
rows.name: You haven't noticed?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0013
rows.name: Look... right behind you!

rows.label: qst700903_msg0014
rows.name: Kyaaaah!

rows.label: qst700903_msg0015
rows.name: ...Kagutsuchi.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0016
rows.name:
That was a little mean,
don't you think?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0017
rows.name:
I'm sorry. I didn't think
she would fall for it.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0018
rows.name:
Laura-sama, there are no
ghosts, right? Right?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0019
rows.name:
Kasumi, you really can't handle
these kinds of stories.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0020
rows.name:
It's okay. Even if there was
one, I'd chase it away for you.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0021
rows.name:
There, there, Kagutsuchi. Don't
look like a scolded child.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0022
rows.name:
I was a little happy to see
an unexpected side of you.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0023
rows.name: Your Majesty...

rows.label: qst700903_msg0024
rows.name:
...Hey, are we going to continue
with this awkward atmosphere?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0025
rows.name: I get it, I get it.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0026
rows.name:
Anyway, further pursuit
is difficult. Let's go
back and report for now.
